                    <div class="section-badge" style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 50px; background: rgba(197,160,89,0.1); color: #c5a059; border: 1px solid rgba(197,160,89,0.2); margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        <i class="bi bi-stars"></i> Ethiopia's #1 AI Learning Platform
                    </div>
                    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                        Unlock Knowledge in Your <span style="color: #c5a059;">Native Language.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 40px;">
                        Master Grade 9–12 subjects with AI tutors who speak Amharic, Afan Oromo, and English.
                    </p>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px;">
                        <a href="/Users/Signup" style="background: #2563eb; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Start Learning — Free</a>
